skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: georgia tech roster
des:
Trying to figure out who just made that amazing play? GA Tech Roster was made to help you figure out which player you're seeing. 

Identify players by jersey number, or get additional information about the players you're watching such as their position, hometown, height, and more. 

Disclaimer: This alexa skill and creator are in no way affiliated with the Georgia Institute of Technology or their football association.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
